msg: Begin teaching ra_serf *not* to use wcprops unnecessarily.
(end_report): If we detect server HTTP v2 support, don't bother
consulting the wcprops cache -- just build our own delta base
URLs.  Add/tweak some nearby comments, too.

the server.  But *do* continue to sanity-check the MERGE response
(even if there's no push_wc_prop callback available).
